GPS_Reader - package GPS_Reader
The package consists of the classes which is related to the GPS and processes the information The package contains CoordinateProcessor.java : to process the coordinates and return the correct result, GpsConnector.java : to connect to the GPS by port and get the information, and NMEAProcessor.java : to process the information given by GpsConnector.java.
GpsConnector - Class in GPS_Reader
A class to connect to GPS-Device and receive the information as Strings.
GpsConnector() - Constructor for class GPS_Reader.GpsConnector
 
GUI - package GUI
The packages consists of the classes which provide Graphical User Interface for the user showing map and first loading screen are involved with this package.
